<section class="page-header">
  <h1 class="project-name">ember-line-graph</h1>
  <h2 class="project-tagline">ember-line-graph is a tiny(1.74kb gzipped), zero-dependency ember-addon to draw line-charts.</h2>
  <a href="https://github.com/astronomersiva/ember-line-graph" class="btn">View on GitHub</a>
